{"tid":2073874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當年日本人攻佔香港 點對香港人？ 終於有人證","createTime":"2020-06-21T15:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T18:33:29.000Z","uid":42246,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"99992c356050a5fbc3e0c3de02f275f877932fd0","tid":2073874,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:57:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZCjhH8i5yro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZCjhH8i5yro&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2YzDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=a4c8880f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZCjhH8i5yro</a><br />\n<br />\n55秒個呀伯 親身體驗<br />\n<br />\n之前睇唔少連登仔話自己呀爺呀麻講 日本仔派糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後重點 香港人老撚左最遺憾就係成世人都窮<br />\n大家記得借鏡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外點解個個都有幾個老婆+幾個情人<br />\n而我就冇女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd5e8d156378da8d331d46b1dc92c196b595277","tid":2073874,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86fa2c133a8d0bcde1ed6e351b9758b97935c2da","tid":2073874,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f21c57e0afc767a0990e1f8cc459b5dbe36090e5","tid":2073874,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T16:01:45.000Z","msg":"港父死偽毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd153431f472fcac0f1b7ad77fa4fd58dbd3a68","tid":2073874,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f